Package: eventviz
Version: 0.1.0
Title: Event Log Visualisation
Description: Visualise any timestamped event log as a location-band timeline,
    a staircase diagram for linear stage processes, faceted cohort
    comparisons, or aggregate/statistical summaries. Originally built for
    patient journeys through clinical locations, but equally suited to any
    process where a case occupies one exclusive state at a time - a
    complaint moving through handling stages, a support ticket through
    statuses, an order through an approval pipeline.
